headline: Northrop Wins $97.5M Deal to Support F-35 APG-85 Radar System

headline: Lockheed Martin Announces Third Quarter 2025 Earnings Results Webcast
summary: Lockheed Martin (NYSE: LMT) will webcast live its third quarter 2025 earnings results conference call (listen-only mode) on Tuesday, Oct. 21, 2025, at 11 a.m. ET. Jim Taiclet, chairman, president and CEO; Evan Scott, chief financial officer; and Maria Ricciardone, vice president, Treasurer and Investor Relations, will discuss third quarter 2025 results, provide updates on key topics and answer questions. Third quarter 2025 results will be published prior to the market opening on Oct. 21.
